==Russian==

===Noun===
'''раз''' (raz) {{m}}, [[разы]] (razý) {{p}}

# [[time]]
#:*{{RUchar|[[два#Russian|два]] ра́за}} — ''twice''
#:*{{RUchar|[[ещё]] раз}} — ''once more; one more time''
#:*{{RUchar|[[ни#Russian|ни]] ра́зу}} — ''not once; never''
#:*{{RUchar|[[не#Russian|не]] раз}} — ''repeatedly''
#:*{{RUchar|[[как#Russian|как]] раз}} — ''just; just in time''
# [[one]] ''(in counting off)''
#:*{{RUchar|раз, два, три, [[огонь]]!}} — ''one, two, three, fire!''

